title: Venus Williams rallies to advance to 2nd round in Hong Kong
text: Photo: Kin Cheung, AP Venus Williams of the United States prepares to return a shot against Yuliya Beygelzimer of Ukraine at the WTA Hong Kong Open Tennis tournament in Hong Kong Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015. Venus Williams of the United States prepares to return a shot... HONG KONG (AP) — Venus Williams rallied to beat Yuliya Beygelzimer of Ukraine 2-6, 6-4, 6-4 Tuesday in the opening round of the Hong Kong Open.
